Je bois pas de café.

76
00:07:08,882 --> 00:07:09,924
Un thé ?

77
00:07:11,342 --> 00:07:12,427
Un chocolat.

78
00:07:12,594 --> 00:07:13,678
Maintenant ?

79
00:07:14,554 --> 00:07:15,972
Demain ou...

80
